  1.48 - 20100827 Added <trim_trigger_file_suffix> tag, which will remove things like .dat or .txt from end of file name when constructing trigger file name. Set to 1 to trim once like ".dat", set to 2 to trim twice like ".dat.gz", etc.  J. Hess.
